he guns in his checked baggage?  Airlines should have picked them up on scans.\n\n\nAfter getting to DC, did he cross over to Virginia to buy the guns at a pawn shop?  Would they sell to someone that only had a California address / ID?\n\n\nOR ... was there someone in DC who provided the guns to him?\n\n\n\n", "author": "11GenAm", "created": 1777181677489, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "iamstadter", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "The guns --- how did he have them?", "last_comment_created": 1777184761409, "content": "<p>Did the shooter own the guns in California?  How did he get them to DC?  Did he drive a car all that way?  Did he fly?  Were the guns in his checked baggage?  Airlines should have picked them up on scans.</p>\n<p>After getting to DC, did he cross over to Virginia to buy the guns at a pawn shop?  Would they sell to someone that only had a California address / ID?</p>\n<p>OR ... was there someone in DC who provided the guns to him?</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 32, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2048246697923428583", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZaO5Ynp", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 37, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "yes", "id": 8581991, "raw_content": "", "author": "DebunkTheLeft", "created": 1777178695734, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "